    • Method Detail

      • union

        public static OntologyMultiheteroset union(OntologyMultiheteroset multiheteroset1,
                                           OntologyMultiheteroset multiheteroset2)
        Method that returns the union of two multiheterosets. The union of two multiheterosets A and B is a multiheteroset with the elements of A and B, where the count of every element is the maximum of its counts in A and B.
        Parameters:
        multiheteroset1 - a multiheteroset.
        multiheteroset2 - a multiheteroset.
        Returns:
        a new multiheteroset that is the union of the multiheterosets multiheteroset1 and multiheteroset2.

      • intersection

        public static OntologyMultiheteroset intersection(OntologyMultiheteroset multiheteroset1,
                                                  OntologyMultiheteroset multiheteroset2)
        Method that returns the intersection of two multiheterosets. The intersection of two multiheterosets A and B is a multiheteroset with the common elements of A and B, where the count of every element is the minimum of its counts in A and B.
        Parameters:
        multiheteroset1 - a multiheteroset.
        multiheteroset2 - a multiheteroset.
        Returns:
        a new multiheteroset that is the intersection of the multiheterosets multiheteroset1 and multiheteroset2.
